text: China’s unusual new coronavirus testing policy has health experts baffled. It requires inbound travelers to show negative results from an antibody test — which can't reliably rule out infections nor prove that a person is not transmitting the virus. https://t.co/kdzdy0xEbo

text:
RT @jacknicas: I wrote about Tommy Heinsohn, the Boston Celtics great whose love for basketball was infectious.

For 40 years behind the mic, he shouted, rooted and excoriated the refs. And we loved him for it.

To the last true unabashed homer: We'll miss you.
